      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">26.206</ph> Solicitation provision
and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1694e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1717e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The contracting officer shall
insert the provision at <xref href="52.226-3.dita#FAR_52_226_3"
                        base="i1055015"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.226-3</xref>,
Disaster or Emergency Area Representation, in solicitations involving
the local area set-aside. For commercial
products and commercial services, see <xref href="12.301.dita#FAR_12_301"
                        base="i1113145"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">12.301</xref>(e)(4).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1717e21" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.226-4.dita#FAR_52_226_4"
                        base="i1055038"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.226-4</xref>, Notice of Disaster
or Emergency Area Set-aside in solicitations and contracts involving
local area set-asides.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1717e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.226-5.dita#FAR_52_226_5"
                        base="i1055048"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.226-5</xref>, Restrictions
on Subcontracting Outside Disaster or Emergency Area, in all solicitations
and contracts that involve local area set-asides.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
